author: Madeline MacGregor
title: Cabin Creek Rest Area northbound reopened
text:
Cabin Creek Rest Area northbound reopened Cabin Creek Rest Area northbound reopened 
Posted on: October 22nd,   
UPDATE, 6:00 p.m. Staff report that Cabin Creek rest area has now reopened following repairs to the water-lines. Thank you for your patience. 
The OTE managed Cabin Creek Rest Area on I-5 is (Milepost 148) is closed temporarily in order to repair a water-line. As soon as the repairs are completed, we will let you know. The next closest rest stop I-5 northbound is Gettings Creek, near Springfield. Share this post:
